\section{Codespaces Investigation}

GitHub Codespaces contains:
\begin{codebox}
\begin{lstlisting}
yosys
nextpnr-ice40
icepack
\end{lstlisting}
\end{codebox}

\begin{problembox}{Missing Toolchain}
\begin{lstlisting}
