symbiflow_synth
symbiflow_write_bitstream
\end{lstlisting}
Therefore, QuickLogic FPGA projects \textbf{cannot} be compiled in this environment.
\end{problembox}

The existing \texttt{blink.bin} is built for the \textbf{Ice40} FPGA and is \textbf{incompatible} with the QuickLogic Pygmy FPGA.

