\subsection*{Upload Failure}
Compilation succeeded; however, the ESP32 bootloader did not accept serial communication.

\begin{problembox}{Symptoms}
\begin{itemize}
  \item Bootloader not responding
  \item Serial synchronization failure
  \item Upload never started
  \item ESP32 rejected incoming serial data
\end{itemize}
The issue occurred during the \textbf{upload stage}, not compilation.
\end{problembox}

